snippet.title: LION DOS/PC Game~ gameplay
snippet.description: Well so sense the LION i downloaded doesnt have audio i decided to put some of my own music into the vid so it would almost seem like audio from the game :D   Yeah so towards the end I just got bored of playing and decided to quit so yeah hope u guys enjoy ;P
